These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, baking
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, teacher
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, juicesy
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, polish
2 different pets are kept: snake, pony
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, taxi
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
2. the teacher is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the owner of the snake is the polish##1
5. the person watching juicesy movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | juice     | mirinda       |
| Hobby         | chess   | baking     |
| Job           | bartender | teacher   |
| Movie-Genre   | juicesy   | martial-arts  |
| Nationality   | polish | japanese |
| Pet           | snake      | pony     |
| Transport     | taxi    | ship   |

