.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, filmmaking
The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, accountant
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, d&b
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, thai
2 different pets are kept: rat, bird
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, roller
1. the accountant is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the owner of the bird is the person driving the roller##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the fan of funk##1
4. the thai is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | lemonade |
| Hobby         | filmmaking        | reading  |
| Job           | software-developer | accountant  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b            | funk    |
| Nationality   | brazilian     | thai   |
| Pet           | rat         | bird    |
| Transport     | scooter           | roller      |

